01:26.753 --> 01:29.488
(siren whoops, radio chatter)

01:29.490 --> 01:32.524
Hey.
Zach, this, uh, fiend here
is thomas ford--

01:32.526 --> 01:34.827
My friend, former roommate,
and general hell-raiser.
(gurney clacks)

01:34.829 --> 01:37.529
Welcome, thomas ford.
What, uh, is the problem?

01:37.531 --> 01:38.831
Um, ford flew commercial

01:38.833 --> 01:40.265
From the central
south african republic

01:40.267 --> 01:41.667
With some apparent
leg trouble.

01:41.669 --> 01:43.268
Exactly. I traveled
thousands of miles,

01:43.270 --> 01:45.671
And he's mad because
I screwed up his plans with who?

01:45.673 --> 01:47.473
Alex.
Alex. Alex?

01:47.475 --> 01:49.541
I don't know.
I stopped at dawn, buddy.
(chuckles)

01:49.543 --> 01:51.210
You met alex, ford.

01:51.212 --> 01:52.177
We had four bottles of wine,
and you tried to kiss her.

01:52.179 --> 01:53.412
Yeah, I don't remember names

01:53.414 --> 01:54.680
Until I'm sure they'll stick,
my friend.

01:54.682 --> 01:56.281
So what do you do over there

01:56.283 --> 01:58.517
In the central
south african republic?
I take pictures.

01:58.519 --> 02:00.819
You ever see that photo
of the, uh, woman in karachi

02:00.821 --> 02:02.688
Holding her child--
the one with the, um--

02:02.690 --> 02:03.622
With the eyes
in front of the thing--

02:03.624 --> 02:05.491
You took that?
Yeah.

02:05.493 --> 02:07.292
I got it, I got it,
I got the leg.
(grunts) thanks, charles.

02:07.294 --> 02:09.294
My hero.
(grunts) all right.

02:09.296 --> 02:11.897
Start a dopamine drip
and get him pip tazo.

02:11.899 --> 02:14.566
So what happened? You, uh,
get shot over there?

02:14.568 --> 02:15.734
No. I got hit by a truck.

02:15.736 --> 02:17.169
Got too close to the action.

02:17.171 --> 02:18.170
They patched me up
in a field hospital,

02:18.172 --> 02:19.371
But I had a sense I should

02:19.373 --> 02:21.306
Get home to a real doctor.
Scissors.

02:21.308 --> 02:22.875
He flew like this?
He greased
the flight attendants.

02:22.877 --> 02:24.309
Charles,
my straight-laced chum.

02:24.311 --> 02:26.678
Open up the present.
You'll see why.

